story.text: Visited Tippet on Monday night to see old friends. THen again this morning picked up a friend to show around the valley. Was a good day. I really do not love the battle of being a litigator - at least not yet. It is very stressful, and with no wins under my belt, I am anxious to see the fruits of my labor.
